                  <summary>1 copy of Fuṣūṣ al-ḥikam</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85129649" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_992-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Ḥall al-Fuṣūṣ (حل الفصوص), a commentary by an unnamed author on 
                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_95223177" role="aut">Ibn al-ʻArabī</persName>’s 
                <title key="work_21822">Fuṣūṣ al-ḥikam</title>. Copy extends as far as ḥikmah of Khālid.
                        </p>
                        <p>19 lines per page; good nastaʻlīq; copyist 
                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f7785" role="scr">ʻAbd Allāh ibn Aḥmad ʻAlī</persName>; rubrications; gold and blue ruled margins; remargined; worm-eaten and discoloured.
                        </p>
                        <p>Dated Kashmir, 19 Zū al-Qaʻdah 999 (8 Sept 1591).</p>
                     </note>
                     <author/>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21822">Ḥall al-Fuṣūṣ</title>
